title: Atlas V delivers Mexican satellite to orbit to complete ULA's 100th launch
text:
Published By: Florida Today: Space - Today 
An Atlas V rocket delivered Mexico's Morelos-3 satellite to orbit after a 6:28 a.m. Friday blastoff from Cape Canaveral. ...
